    <ol style="color: #000000; margin: 0;">
      <li>The device (NAS, router, etc.) sends logs to port 514</li>
      <li>rsyslog receives and filters them according to the configured rules</li>
      <li>The logs are written to separate files</li>
      <li>The Wazuh agent monitors those files</li>
      <li>The logs are sent to the Wazuh server for analysis</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

